txt.en: 'Do you think they'll find us here?'
'What of that Man, though? He promised freedom if we fought on the side of the Dark Lord.'
'Let us send this one away that we may be alone once more...'
'You're not like the last one... the Man of Umbar.'
'The King may speak for us, but he cannot force us to fight!'
'He thought us unworthy, but when we raze the rest of the vale, he will think again!'
'We fled last time, and so we shall again.'
'He promises only lies, and the others are fools to believe him.'
'Those that follow Isildur's heir may see their oaths fulfilled, but the others shall never find rest.'
